videos.description: Nick Dowd gets Miami (OH) on the board with an 18-yard field goal early in the first quarter against Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Miami (OH) settles for field goal on opening drive

videos.description: As Miami (OH) works its way downfield, Mississippi State is able to force a fumble and gain possession of the ball.
videos.headline: Mississippi State forces fumble against Miami (OH)

videos.description: Gus Ragland finds James Gardner in the end zone for a 6-yard touchdown, giving Miami (OH) a 9-0 lead over Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Miami (OH) WR reels in TD catch over defender

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald fakes the handoff and rushes two yards for the Bulldogs' first touchdown of the afternoon.
videos.headline: Mississippi State cuts into Miami (OH)'s lead before halftime

videos.description: Halftime interview with Miami head coach Chuck Martin
videos.headline: Halftime interview with Miami head coach Chuck Martin

videos.description: Gus Ragland pass complete to James Gardner for 20 yds to the MisSt 3 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: G. Ragland pass to J. Gardner for 20 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Miami (OH) quarterback Gus Ragland uses a nice play-action fake before throwing to tight end Ryan Smith for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Miami (OH) tight end Smith grabs 1-yard TD

videos.description: Mississippi State quarterback Nick Fitzgerald runs the zone read to perfection, running down the far sidelines 44 yards into the end zone.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald scampers 44 yards to the house

videos.description: Gus Ragland pass intercepted Jamoral Graham return for 21 yds to the MisSt 30, Gus Ragland throws his first INT of his college career
videos.headline: G. Ragland pass intercepted by J. Graham return  for 21 yds

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald run for 27 yds to the MISSSTATE 37 for a 1ST down MIAMI OH Penalty, Personal Foul (Deondre Daniels) to the MiaOh 22 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: N. Fitzgerald run for 27 yds for a 1ST down,MIAMI OH Personal Foul on D. Daniels for targeting

videos.description: Westin Graves kicks a 36-yard field goal to give Mississippi State its first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Mississippi State takes lead after field goal

videos.description: Miami (OH) DB Deondre Daniels gets disqualified from the game after using the crown of his helmet to the head area of Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Miami (OH) defender ejected for targeting QB

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miami (OH) defender ejected for targeting QB) 2016/12/26 ESHEET

videos.description: Gus Ragland pass complete to James Gardner for 23 yds to the MisSt 17 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: G. Ragland pass to J. Gardner for 23 yds for a 1ST down to put Miami(OH)into field goal range late

videos.description: Having already blocked an extra point earlier in the game, Mississippi State blocks the would-be game-winning field goal against Miami (OH) to seal the one-point victory.
videos.headline: Mississippi State blocks field goal to seal victory

videos.description: MSU head coach Dan Mullen talks about his team's 17-16 victory in the St. Petersburg Bowl and how important the offseason will be for QB Nick Fitzgerald.
videos.headline: Mullen: 'We made the play we needed to'

videos.description: Post game interview with Mississippi head coach Dan Mullen just before recieving the St. Petersburg Bowl Trophy
videos.headline: Post game interview with Mississippi head coach Dan Mullen just before recieving the St. Petersburg Bowl Trophy

videos.description: Post game breakdown of Mississippi State's St. Petersburg Bowl victory
videos.headline: Bulldogs rally to win St. Petersburg Bowl 17-16
